    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm just saying, it's really hard for me to sleep right now and the diazepam by itself isn't quite doing it. if i just took a half dose of the pill and had the glass of wine, would that be more manageable? i just need to find a way to actually get some rest tonight.",
